# --- Hand-authored eternal node descriptions ---
mastery.acr_eternal.desc = Each purchase nudges your acrobatics mastery bonus-drop chance higher; each costs more than the last. Grind without limit.
mastery.enc_eternal.desc = Each purchase nudges your enchanting mastery bonus-drop chance higher; each costs more than the last. Grind without limit.
mastery.fb_eternal.desc = Each purchase stokes Fireball's damage a little further; each costs more than the last.
mastery.fis_eternal.desc = Each purchase nudges your fishing mastery bonus-drop chance higher; each costs more than the last. Grind without limit.
mastery.har_eternal.desc = Each purchase nudges your harvesting mastery bonus-drop chance higher; each costs more than the last. Grind without limit.
mastery.met_eternal.desc = Each purchase shaves Meteor's cooldown and stokes its damage; each costs more than the last.
mastery.min_eternal.desc = Each purchase nudges your mining mastery bonus-drop chance higher; each costs more than the last. Grind without limit.
mastery.ps_eternal.desc = Each purchase sharpens Piercing Shot's damage (swing and cast); each costs more than the last.
mastery.sst_eternal.desc = Each purchase shaves Shadowstep's cooldown; each costs more than the last.
mastery.ss_eternal.desc = Each purchase hardens Shield Slam's damage; each costs more than the last.
mastery.ww_eternal.desc = Each purchase whets Whirlwind's damage (swing and cast); each costs more than the last.
mastery.woo_eternal.desc = Each purchase nudges your woodcutting mastery bonus-drop chance higher; each costs more than the last. Grind without limit.

